---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import BookingWidget from '../components/BookingWidget.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About Ice Cap Labs | AI Automation for Service Businesses | Wichita, KS" description="Founded by a former service business owner, Ice Cap Labs builds AI automation systems for HVAC, plumbing, and electrical companies in Wichita, Kansas. Real experience solving real problems.">

  <!-- PAGE TITLE -->
  <header class="page-header">
    <h1 class="page-title word-reveal">About</h1>
  </header>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section id="about-hero" style="background: var(--bg-void);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header reveal">
        <h2 class="section-title word-reveal" data-delay="0.05" style="font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem); color: var(--accent);">Ice Cap Labs</h2>
      </div>
      <div style="max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;">
        <p class="reveal" style="font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--text-primary); line-height: 1.85;">
          A service dedicated to delivering unique automation solutions. Powered by a hard-working local expert programmer, Ice Cap Labs is a flexible and agile service ready to accept challenges of all scales while leveraging the capabilities of contemporary automation.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TILE STRIP -->
  <section id="tile-strip-founder" style="background: var(--bg-void); padding: 0;">
    <div class="tile-grid" id="tile-grid-founder"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- FOUNDER -->
  <section id="founder-top" style="background: #000; padding-bottom: 0;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="founder-section">
        <h2 class="founder-name reveal" style="font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem); color: var(--accent);">Maxwell Hinman</h2>

        <img src="/max-phone-wide.png" alt="Maxwell Hinman — Founder of Ice Cap Labs" class="founder-image reveal" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section id="founder-bottom" style="background: #26a6eb; padding-top: 10rem; margin-top: -8rem;">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem); max-width: 960px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;">

        <!-- Mission -->
        <div class="reveal">
          <ion-icon name="rocket-outline" style="font-size: 64px; color: #000; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;"></ion-icon>
          <h3 style="color: #000; font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Mission</h3>
          <p style="color: #000; font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.75;">
            To be the go-to automation partner for businesses that need reliable, custom-built solutions. Think automation, think Ice Cap Labs.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Vision -->
        <div class="reveal">
          <ion-icon name="eye-outline" style="font-size: 64px; color: #000; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;"></ion-icon>
          <h3 style="color: #000; font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Vision</h3>
          <p style="color: #000; font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.75;">
            Sustainable, strategic growth that creates real value for every client. Building partnerships, not just projects.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- VALUES -->
  <section id="values" style="background: var(--bg-void); padding: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 6rem) 0;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header reveal" style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
        <h2 class="section-title word-reveal" data-delay="0.05" style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.25rem);">What We Believe In</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="values-tabs" id="values-tabs">
        <button class="values-tab active" data-value="collaboration">Collaboration</button>
        <button class="values-tab" data-value="trust">Trust</button>
        <button class="values-tab" data-value="quality">Top Quality</button>
        <button class="values-tab" data-value="transparency">Transparency</button>
        <button class="values-tab" data-value="adaptability">Adaptability</button>
        <button class="values-tab" data-value="results">Results</button>
      </div>

      <div class="values-content" id="values-content">
        <div class="values-panel active" data-panel="collaboration">
          <ion-icon name="people-outline" style="font-size: 64px; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;"></ion-icon>
          <p>Great solutions come from working together. We stay closely involved with our clients throughout every project, because the best automation is built through partnership, not handed off.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="values-panel" data-panel="trust">
          <ion-icon name="shield-checkmark-outline" style="font-size: 64px; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;"></ion-icon>
          <p>We do what we say we'll do. No surprises, no runaround. When you work with us, you get honest timelines, honest pricing, and someone who picks up the phone.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="values-panel" data-panel="quality">
          <ion-icon name="diamond-outline" style="font-size: 64px; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;"></ion-icon>
          <p>Every system we build is crafted with care. We don't cut corners or ship half-finished work. Your business deserves automation that's reliable, polished, and built to last.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="values-panel" data-panel="transparency">
          <ion-icon name="eye-outline" style="font-size: 64px; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;"></ion-icon>
          <p>You'll always know what things cost, how long they'll take, and exactly what you're getting. Clear communication from start to finish — no fine print, no hidden fees.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="values-panel" data-panel="adaptability">
          <ion-icon name="sync-outline" style="font-size: 64px; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;"></ion-icon>
          <p>Every business is different. We stay flexible and agile, ready to pivot and adjust as your needs evolve. One-size-fits-all isn't in our vocabulary.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="values-panel" data-panel="results">
          <ion-icon name="trending-up-outline" style="font-size: 64px; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;"></ion-icon>
          <p>At the end of the day, automation should save you time and make you money. We measure success by the real impact our systems have on your business.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- TILE STRIP -->
  <section id="tile-strip">
    <div class="tile-grid" id="tile-grid"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section id="about-cta" style="background: var(--bg-void); padding: 6rem 0;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header reveal" style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
        <p class="section-eyebrow">Let's Talk</p>
        <h2 class="section-title word-reveal">I'd Like to Hear About Your Business</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          No sales pitch or pressure. Just a genuine conversation about what you're dealing with and whether I can help. I'll come visit you, and we'll figure it out together.
        </p>
      </div>
      <BookingWidget title="Schedule a Call" />
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
